{"tid":973984,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[Linux] 任何pc/laptop/tablet/手機做external mon","createTime":"2019-01-08T14:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T04:03:48.000Z","uid":28563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6efb2db7497c2a95d13d6928e764f6680b0082fa","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"效果<br />\n- 得15-30FPS<br />\n- latency 大概0.x秒<br />\n- 唔洗用線，全程wifi<br />\n- 唔夠打機，但絕對夠做野<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/4ad0433de20460357fa96b9e44f2b33cc2919147.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2F4ad0433de20460357fa96b9e44f2b33cc2919147.jpeg&h=241f8d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/4c2bb254df8abb5a93493994499843d964d0d61d.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2F4c2bb254df8abb5a93493994499843d964d0d61d.mp4&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPzghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5df8a5cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://drop.wtako.net/file/4c2bb254df8abb5a93493994499843d964d0d61d.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"56650196cda6c7fcf36ad0d9714e1875eb882bd3","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"Server (laptop) setup:<br />\n1. 裝nomachine，<code># systemctl enable nxserver</code><br />\n(2.) 要手動裝h264，唔裝都得，但會矇d lag d: <code># systemctl stop nxserver</code><br />\n(3.) 跟<a href=\"https://www.nomachine.com/AR09M00863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nomachine.com%2FAR09M00863&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPzghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c1d948aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nomachine.com/AR09M00863</a> setup，intel quicksync support好似要搞一大堆野，不了<br />\n4. <code># systemctl start nxserver</code><br />\n5. 判斷一下client個mon resultion幾多，例如3440x1440<br />\n6. <code>$ gtf 3440 1440 60</code>，會出以下output<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">  # 3440x1440 @ 60.00 Hz (GTF) hsync: 89.40 kHz; pclk: 419.11 MHz\n  Modeline &quot;3440x1440_60.00&quot;  419.11  3440 3688 4064 4688  1440 1441 1444 1490  -HSync +Vsync</code></pre><br />\n7. 將modeline打後既野copy入去做xrandr既argument: <code>$ xrandr --newmode &quot;3440x1440_60.00&quot;  419.11  3440 3688 4064 4688  1440 1441 1444 1490  -HSync +Vsync</code><br />\n8. <code>$ xrandr --addmode VIRTUAL1  &quot;3440x1440_60.00&quot;</code><br />\n9. 去gnome/其他de既display setting咁set<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/a67e019f9176652dc7164aedf56cfa75010c6ff1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fa67e019f9176652dc7164aedf56cfa75010c6ff1.png&h=ca5a6bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(唔同scale要wayland，所以1080p notebook pair 4k mon最好只用1080p)<br />\n10. apply完拍enter，個confirm dialog好大機會出係個virtual mon"},{"pid":"bf92c9da31a7125e90942aacf0471eb43b5a26ec","tid":973984,"uid":3055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"高汁linux user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce45df4381140c57c6bd3ef5ba8c45fde42a593b","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:27:17.000Z","msg":"Client setup:<br />\n1. 裝nomachine<br />\n2. 打開nomachine<br />\n3. 部server應該會自動係client出現，開setting show remote cursor<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/3acea75d897f1415fa4ce393470662d7c9403b86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2F3acea75d897f1415fa4ce393470662d7c9403b86.png&h=0fee9efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 成功連到之後，mouse移去右上，click開setting，change monitor<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/d544436263ac7318fe4218074665ac20c47ad80c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fd544436263ac7318fe4218074665ac20c47ad80c.png&h=4d5ebb2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/42d7ebb8dbd80d906456dc278df1d88c5485afc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2F42d7ebb8dbd80d906456dc278df1d88c5485afc7.png&h=883332a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/fae2473f8ba3cb24edca135a0be19d7a2eb5e3b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Ffae2473f8ba3cb24edca135a0be19d7a2eb5e3b7.png&h=56436fba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"191e03a9912cca488c2d35f7ff1c03f8d0348e58","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"試緊ipad client........."},{"pid":"c99ae8d0bcb0d19037c7bc3c8d58a224a82484dd","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf92c9da31a7125e90942aacf0471eb43b5a26ec","tid":973984,"uid":3055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"高汁linux user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"高汁搵唔到食的"},{"pid":"645ece447cb6dfb4869f69192819ac4204cb6958","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/da630e3e1d8549430bfc9250f5d02bf72e260843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fda630e3e1d8549430bfc9250f5d02bf72e260843.jpg&h=8cfd4cb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff1f02dccd4464980fc0340dfc26d80deb5b3759","tid":973984,"uid":13917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"用咩notebook裝linux"},{"pid":"fe81a3280e94bb42944e64bc30d05f559b45a0a9","tid":973984,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff1f02dccd4464980fc0340dfc26d80deb5b3759","tid":973984,"uid":13917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"用咩notebook裝linux"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"xps13"},{"pid"